<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالْغَمَامِ}</span> ... بِالسَّحَابِ الأَبْيَضِ الرَّقِيقِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبِيلًا}</span> ... طَرِيقًا إِلَى الجَنَّةِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَرَتَّلْنَاهُ}</span> ... بَيَّنَّاهُ فِي تَثَبُّتٍ وَمُهْلَةٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
